title.rendered: SUPREMA BIOLITE N2 OUTDOOR IP FINGERPRINT TERMINAL

content.rendered:
Suprema BioLite N2 is a Suprema’s 2nd generation outdoor fingerprint terminal that provides comprehensive access control and time attendance features based on Suprema’s latest biometric technology and security platform.

Features

  • Faster Fingerprint Matching Speed
  • High-precision OP6 optical sensor / IP67 Certified Dust & Water Protection / Full Time Attendance Features
  • Communicates with Smartphones
  • Dual Frequency, Multi-Smartcard Reader
  • Versatile Interface.
